id isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/kibbutz-security-squad-member-who-killed-suspected-thief-wont-face-trial/00000191-bf0b-d2e0-a7d5-bfdb3da80000</guid></item><item><title>前人质敦促以色列总统谴责内塔尼亚胡的玩忽职守</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/former-hostage-urges-israeli-president-to-call-out-netanyahus-dereliction-of-duty/00000191-bef7-d9c6-a997-beff55930000</link><description>利亚特·阿齐利在前总统西蒙·佩雷斯的官方纪念仪式上发表讲话：“内塔尼亚胡反对我们支持人质协议的以色列公民，并将我们视为威胁——这是他政治生存所需的毒药。”我们是一个被内外破坏者绑架的国家”</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 21:57:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/former-hostage-urges-israeli-president-to-call-out-netanyahus-dereliction-of-duty/00000191-bef7-d9c6-a997-beff55930000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击中丧生的一个以色列家庭的四名成员在贝埃里基布兹安息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/four-members-of-one-israeli-family-killed-on-october-7-laid-to-rest-in-kibbutz-beeri/00000191-be6a-dd1b-a7db-bffe74000000</link><description>10 月 7 日被谋杀的 Heztroni 家族的四名成员被重新安葬在贝埃里基布兹：12 岁的双胞胎 Liel 和 Yanai，以及抚养他们的年迈的祖父母 Ayala 和 Avia</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 19:51:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/four-members-of-one-israeli-family-killed-on-october-7-laid-to-rest-in-kibbutz-beeri/00000191-be6a-dd1b-a7db-bffe74000000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯并不是以色列内部裂痕的始作俑者，分裂也不仅仅是外部敌人造成的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-09-04/ty-article/.highlight/how-to-stop-peaceniks-from-falling-into-hamas-trap-of-holding-israeli-leaders-to-account/00000191-be0c-de0a-afd5-fe4c2b510000</link><description>毫无疑问，哈马斯利用人质进行宣传。但内塔尼亚胡所说的哈马斯利用内部分歧在以色列制造分裂并不是哈马斯的发明，这种分裂不仅仅是外部敌人造成的</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 19:26:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-09-04/ty-article/.highlight/how-to-stop-peaceniks-from-falling-into-hamas-trap-of-holding-israeli-leaders-to-account/00000191-be0c-de0a-afd5-fe4c2b510000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国家档案馆直到 2089 年才会披露内塔尼亚胡寄出的信件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-state-archives-wont-reveal-letters-sent-by-netanyahu-until-2089/00000191-be0f-dc3b-a7df-ff5f24fd0000</link><description>档案馆以隐私问题为由，密封了内塔尼亚胡写给多位知名人士的私人信件，尽管此前已批准公开类似的信件。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 18:33:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-state-archives-wont-reveal-letters-sent-by-netanyahu-until-2089/00000191-be0f-dc3b-a7df-ff5f24fd0000</guid></item><item><title>伴随脊髓灰质炎疫苗进入加沙的阴谋论</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/the-conspiracy-theory-accompanying-the-polio-vaccine-into-gaza/00000191-bdfc-dd1b-a7db-bffe3f160000</link><description>备受瞩目的加沙活动家 Bisan Owda 并不信任以色列已经签署的脊髓灰质炎疫苗。但包括医疗专业人士在内的许多网上人士建议这位获得艾美奖提名的网红删除她的视频并道歉，以免脊髓灰质炎在拉斯维加斯大道蔓延</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 18:16:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/the-conspiracy-theory-accompanying-the-polio-vaccine-into-gaza/00000191-bdfc-dd1b-a7db-bffe3f160000</guid></item><item><title>“恐惧感”：哥伦比亚大学新年伊始，犹太和以色列学生保持警惕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-09-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/sense-of-dread-jewish-and-israeli-students-wary-as-columbia-u-starts-new-year/00000191-bd2e-de3d-abb7-ff6fd3e60000</link><description>虽然纽约常春藤盟校坚称已采取新程序来制止反犹太主义和去年加沙战争引发的丑陋场面的重演，但犹太学生和教职员工表示，他们已经看到了事情“正在好转”的迹象。他们离开的地方&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 17:45:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-09-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/sense-of-dread-jewish-and-israeli-students-wary-as-columbia-u-starts-new-year/00000191-bd2e-de3d-abb7-ff6fd3e60000</guid></item><item><title>“内塔尼亚胡的母亲对拉宾批准恩德培而不是达成协议感到愤怒”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-09-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/netanyahus-mom-was-furious-at-rabin-for-approving-entebbe-instead-of-reaching-a-deal/00000191-bcce-de3d-abb7-feef359a0000</link><description>新系列纪录片《人质》的创作者讲述了我们如何遭遇 100 多名以色列人质在哈马斯的囚禁中死去近一年的情况</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 17:37:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-09-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/netanyahus-mom-was-furious-at-rabin-for-approving-entebbe-instead-of-reaching-a-deal/00000191-bcce-de3d-abb7-feef359a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质家属称亲内塔尼亚胡频道告诉他们联盟胜过协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostages-families-say-pro-netanyahu-channel-told-them-coalition-trumps-deal/00000191-bd90-dffe-abf9-bdff65c90000</link><description>Channel 14 高管告诉家属，释放亲人的协议不会达成，因为这会导致政府垮台</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 17:11:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostages-families-say-pro-netanyahu-channel-told-them-coalition-trumps-deal/00000191-bd90-dffe-abf9-bdff65c90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 334 天：大约 70 枚火箭从黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-334-some-70-rockets-fired-at-north-israel-from-lebanon/00000191-bdf0-dc3b-a7df-fff0b3620001</link><description>政府消息人士告诉《国土报》，内塔尼亚胡几周前决定不达成释放人质协议，并以费城走廊为借口破坏谈判。据《华尔街日报》报道，预计将提交更详细的人质/停火协议草案 ■ 这是战争开始 334 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 17:00:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-334-some-70-rockets-fired-at-north-israel-from-lebanon/00000191-bdf0-dc3b-a7df-fff0b3620001</guid></item><item><title>为什么哈马斯试图隐瞒被以色列杀害的武装分子人数</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-09-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-hamas-tries-to-hide-the-number-of-its-members-killed/00000191-bd7b-d13c-a39b-bfff809b0000</link><description>所有加沙人都知道不要发布被杀的哈马斯战士的信息，任何违反这一规则的人都有可能给该组织以及以色列带来麻烦</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 16:57:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-09-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-hamas-tries-to-hide-the-number-of-its-members-killed/00000191-bd7b-d13c-a39b-bfff809b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列教育部禁止学校举办以色列-巴勒斯坦遇难者家庭论坛</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/education-ministry-bans-schools-from-hosting-israeli-palestinian-bereaved-families-forum/00000191-bd5b-d227-aff3-bfdbb1fe0000</link><description>以色列教育部无视耶路撒冷地方法院的命令，冻结了一个“对话遭遇”计划，该计划由一个将失去亲人的巴勒斯坦和以色列家庭聚集在一起的组织运营。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 16:22:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/education-ministry-bans-schools-from-hosting-israeli-palestinian-bereaved-families-forum/00000191-bd5b-d227-aff3-bfdbb1fe0000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔交通事故调查员出席部长聚会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/investigator-of-ben-gvirs-traffic-accident-attended-ministers-party/00000191-bd07-dc3b-a7df-ff57acfd0000</link><description>负责该部门的警官预计将就这起事故起诉本-格维尔的司机 ■ 警方表示，他只在现场出现了几分钟，且原因无关</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 14:48:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/investigator-of-ben-gvirs-traffic-accident-attended-ministers-party/00000191-bd07-dc3b-a7df-ff57acfd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方关闭特拉维夫抗议空域以“监控空中交通”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-to-close-airspace-over-tel-aviv-protest-to-monitor-air-traffic/00000191-bd15-d13c-a39b-bf9db7d70000</link><description>来自“示范无人机巡逻队”的无人机传单在过去两年里一直在从上方记录演示，他们声称这是一个旨在让他们更难操作的步骤</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 14:12:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-to-close-airspace-over-tel-aviv-protest-to-monitor-air-traffic/00000191-bd15-d13c-a39b-bf9db7d70000</guid></item><item><title>愤怒的以色列人正在抗议以拯救人质。他们能改变内塔尼亚胡的想法吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/furious-israelis-are-protesting-to-save-the-hostages-can-they-change-netanyahus-mind/00000191-bc49-d9c6-a997-be6996320000</link><description>自周日以来，以色列人为人质发起了大规模的公民动员：数十万人走上街头，举行总罢工。尽管哈马斯杀害了更多人质，但示威者并不能迫使内塔尼亚胡政府放弃对一项挽救生命的协议的抵制</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 14:07:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/furious-israelis-are-protesting-to-save-the-hostages-can-they-change-netanyahus-mind/00000191-bc49-d9c6-a997-be6996320000</guid></item><item><title>以色列财政部长突然腾出时间制定国家预算</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/israels-finance-minister-suddenly-finds-time-for-the-state-budget/00000191-bd19-de3d-abb7-ff7bdc6c0000</link><description>在一再拖延之后，斯莫特里奇决定是时候公布 2025 年的支出计划了。他是终于清醒过来了，还是陷入了恐慌？</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 13:18:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/israels-finance-minister-suddenly-finds-time-for-the-state-budget/00000191-bd19-de3d-abb7-ff7bdc6c0000</guid></item><item><title>我父亲是加沙的人质。我必须恳求内塔尼亚胡拯救他吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/my-father-is-a-hostage-in-gaza-do-i-have-to-beg-netanyahu-to-save-him/00000191-bcec-db99-a1d1-bdfe774c0000</link><description>早在十月份，我们就非常确信我们的政府会尽一切努力拯救人质，首先是从最脆弱的人开始，比如你，爸爸。我听到你告诉我：“救救孩子们吧，我已经过上了充实的生活。”但内塔尼亚胡政府并没有拯救孩子们，也没有拯救你这个84岁的老人</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 12:47:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/my-father-is-a-hostage-in-gaza-do-i-have-to-beg-netanyahu-to-save-him/00000191-bcec-db99-a1d1-bdfe774c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军告诉家长，黎巴嫩边境 75% 的以色列军队观察员已从前线撤离</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/75-of-israeli-army-spotters-on-lebanese-border-moved-from-frontline-idf-tells-parents/00000191-bca1-dd1b-a7db-bfff62bc0000</link><description>以色列国防军观察员的父母向以色列高等法院请愿，回应驻黎巴嫩边境观察员的投诉，称他们的基地在真主党袭击中避难所不足，并且担心类似于哈马斯 10 月 7 日对纳哈尔奥兹军事哨所实施的袭击</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 11:53:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/75-of-israeli-army-spotters-on-lebanese-border-moved-from-frontline-idf-tells-parents/00000191-bca1-dd1b-a7db-bfff62bc0000</guid></item></channel></rss>